{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.log()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/log","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/debug\"><code>debug()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/error\"><code>error()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/info\"><code>info()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Console API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Gibt eine Nachricht auf der Web-Konsole aus.</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Hinweis:</strong> Dieses Feature ist in <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a> verfügbar</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.log(<em>obj1</em> [, <em>obj2</em>, ..., <em>objN</em>]);\nconsole.log(<em>msg</em> [, <em>subst1</em>, ..., <em>substN</em>]);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj1\"><code>obj1</code> ... <code>objN</code></dt>\n <dd>Eine Liste von auszugebenden JavaScript-Objekten. Die Zeichenfolgedarstellungen der Objekte werden in der angegebenen Reihenfolge aneinandergehängt und ausgegeben.</dd>\n <dt id=\"msg\"><code>msg</code></dt>\n <dd>Eine JavaScript-Zeichenfolge, die Null oder mehr Ersatzzeichefolgen enthält.</dd>\n <dt id=\"subst1\"><code>subst1</code> ... <code>substN</code></dt>\n <dd>JavaScript-Objekte durch die die Ersatzzeichenfolgen in <code>msg</code> ersetzt werden sollen. Dies gibt Ihnen zusätzliche Kontrolle über die Formatierung der Ausgabe.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Weitere Details finden Sie im Abschnitt <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console#Outputting_text_to_the_console\">Outputting text to the console</a> in der Dokumentation zu <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#log\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Console API<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'console.log()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Erste Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Ersatzzeichenfolgen</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span><br>\n    28<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/9\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-12-20.\">9.0</a> (9.0)</td>\n   <td>10<sup>[2]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Verfügbar in Workers</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/38\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2015-05-19.\">38.0</a> (38.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Ersatzzeichenfolgen</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>9.0 (9.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Verfügbar in Workers</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>38.0 (38.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Weisst man <code>%d</code> einen negativen Wert zu, wird dieser zur nächsten negative Ganzzahl abgerundet; z. B. wird -0.1 zu -1.</p>\n\n<p>[2] <code>%c</code> wird nicht unterstützt; <code>%d</code> wird als 0 angezeigt, falls der Wert keine Nummer ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"unterschied_zu_console.dir()","title":"Unterschied zu console.dir()","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In Firefox generieren beide Kommandos dieselbe Ausgabe, wenn als Parameter ein DOM-Element mitgegeben wird: Man erhält in beiden Fällen eine JSON-artige Baumstruktur.</p>\n\n<p>In Chrome besteht aber bei gleicher Eingabe ein nützlicher Unterschied:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DozDcYR.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>Bemerkung:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>console.log</code> gibt das Element als HTML-artige Baumstruktur aus</li>\n <li><code>console.dir</code>&nbsp;gibt das Element als JSON-artige Baumstruktur aus</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Mit <code>console.log</code> werden DOM-Elemente also speziell behandelt. Bei <code>console.dir</code> ist dies nicht der Fall. Dies ist oft dann nützlich, wenn man die vollständige Darstellung des DOM-JS-Objekts ansehen möchte.</p>\n\n<p>Mehr Informationen dazu finden Sie unter <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/chrome-developer-tools/docs/console-api#consoledirobject\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Chrome Console API reference</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/dragonfly/documentation/console/\" rel=\" noopener\">Opera Dragonfly documentation: Console</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/gg589530\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN: Using the F12 Tools Console to View Errors and Status</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://getfirebug.com/wiki/index.php/Console_API\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Firebug wiki: Console API</a> - FireBug unterstützt noch weitere Features in seiner console.log()-Implementation, wie z. B. <a href=\"http://www.softwareishard.com/blog/firebug/firebug-tip-styled-logging/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">styled logging</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/console.html#console_console_log_data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">NodeJS: Console API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Parameter","id":"parameter"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Unterschied zu console.dir()","id":"unterschied_zu_console.dir()"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Gibt eine Nachricht auf der Web-Konsole aus.","popularity":0.0012,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"console.log()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"console.log","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/console/log","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/console/log/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Console","title":"Console"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Console/log","title":"Console.log()"}],"pageTitle":"Console.log() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}